OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRussian priest investigated
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffor blessing Stalin statue 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A Russian Orthodox priest is under     
OL,6, investigation after he was filmed      
OL,7, blessing a new statue of the Soviet    
OL,8, dictator Joseph Stalin.                
OL,10,FThe incident happened on Tuesday at the
OL,11,Funveiling of the eight-metre (26ft)    
OL,12,Fmonument in the city of Velikiye Luki. 
OL,14,FIn a statement, the priest's local     
OL,15,Fdiocese said his actions did not       
OL,16,Frepresent the church's views.          
OL,18,FStalin ruled the Soviet Union from 1924
OL,19,Funtil 1953 and oversaw a brutal regime 
OL,20,Fthat tried to eliminate religion.      
